{0 day11-solver-pool}

Parallel solving via solver_worker subprocesses. {!Day11_solver_pool.Solver_pool} spawns
multiple out-of-process solver workers to solve packages in parallel,
avoiding any in-process solver dependency. The single entry point
{!Day11_solver_pool.Solver_pool.solve_many} takes a list of target packages and a
parallelism level, distributes work across workers, and collects
results. Supports multi-repository solving, pinned directories, version
constraints, and optional doc-dependency inclusion.

Depends on {!page-solution} for solution result types.

